divs: Sighting DetailsSighting Report: it was march 21 at 9:00p.m.i seen three redish lights to the north of clinton county that was very high in the sky and from my experince i beleive that they were jets or airplanes they lasted about ten to fifteen seconds and then they faded away it was very weird. not falling stars my friend also seen them we were both weided out by them it was when we were parking my car to go into his house. when i did a search on mufon and seen that the family by kirklin indiana had seen somthing similar that they called orange lights and checked with airports to reveal that there wasnt suposed to be anything in the sky i thought i would let you know that i had seen those three lights also but what i saw were red ones we seen them on the north side of frankfort and it looked like they were in carol county not clinton. they were far away.at least that is where they appered to be. very stange
